dc_description_s: This line shapefile contains subprefecture boundaries for the Central African Republic as of January 2007. These are the level 2 administrative units (ADM2) for the Central African Republic. This layer is part of the Map Library dataset containing line and polygon boundaries for individual countries on the African continent.The Map Library is a project of the UK charity â€œThe Map Maker Trust." It aims to make public domain mapping data more readily available for development in all kinds of fields, from health care to urban management, from de-mining to environmental protection.
